title: Thee Marloes performs "Logika" and more Live on KEXP

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Thee Marloes performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded August 1, 2025.

Songs:  
Logika 00:18
Over 03:54
Not Today 08:06
Mungkin Saja 11:47
I'd Be Lost 15:34

Natassya Sianturi - Vocal, Keys

Tommy Satrio - Drums

Audio Engineer: Kevin Suggs
Mastering Engineer: Matt Ogaz

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen, Jonathan Jacobson & Luke Knecht
